<varlistentry id="options.Fullscreen">
	<term>Fullscreen</term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Toggle window Fullscreen state. Will disregard any AvoidCover windows and will try to make window 
		as big as the screen unless it's hints set certain limitation on size. Window in Fullscreen mode cannot be Maximized.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
